                        <td style="width:40%">Member-Secretary.</td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </p>
            <p style="font-weight:bold;">
                District level Implementing Committee for ensuring convergence of other sectores,consisting of:
            </p>
            <p>
                <table width="100%">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width:10%">(a)</td>
                        <td style="width:40%">
                           District Collector.
                        </td>
                        <td style="width:10%">
                            -
                        </td>
                        <td style="width:40%">
                           Chairman
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width:10%">(b)</td>
